Super Death Ray

Code for the game "Super Death Ray" for 48 Hour Contest #8 http://www.wolverinesoft.org/event/contest/48hourcontest8/

The theme for the contest was "Waste"

Demo at http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E3GgKbKhpBw

Screenshot at http://www-personal.umich.edu/~djmcall/screenshot.png

Download available at http://www.wolverinesoft.org/game/170/super-death-ray

Currently unplayable without an Xbox360 controller